b_paragraph\" ><strong>64 Mutations</strong> alter the challenges you face each run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891310/extras/ad3ad852aa3b485a950938b3b0866c5d.avif?t=1772118894\" width=616 height=77 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891310/extras/d237fb3da359521062407403fd284eb3.poster.avif?t=1772118894\" width=616 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891310/extras/d237fb3da359521062407403fd284eb3.webm?t=1772118894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891310/extras/d237fb3da359521062407403fd284eb3.mp4?t=1772118894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20-minute Runs</strong> that can be continued in Endless Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>75 Bassy Electronic Tunes</strong> that adapt to the current mood & intensity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cosmetics</strong> like spider legs and tank tread</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Accessibility Settings</strong> for colourblindness, motion sickness, and even arachnophobia!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 Steam Achievements</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cloud Save</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plays great on Steam Deck!!!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891310/extras/8e9